342
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:44,520
What's going on?

343
00:19:57,360 --> 00:19:58,240
What are you standing for?

344
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:00,640
It's nothing.

345
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:01,840
Sit down.

346
00:20:01,840 --> 00:20:03,680
Finish this ginger tea.

347
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:08,520
I don't like ginger tea.

348
00:20:08,880 --> 00:20:09,560
No.

349
00:20:10,960 --> 00:20:11,920
You got caught in the rain.

350
00:20:12,360 --> 00:20:13,520
You'll get a cold if you don't drink it.

351
00:20:15,040 --> 00:20:15,760
Just leave it here.

352
00:20:15,760 --> 00:20:16,720
I'll drink it later.

353
00:20:16,720 --> 00:20:17,760
It'll be cold soon.

354
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:19,400
I...I'm afraid it might be too hot.

355
00:20:20,760 --> 00:20:21,520
Let me feed you.

356
