Chancellor.

357
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:42,200
The men we sent out didn't succeed.

358
00:20:46,320 --> 00:20:47,360
A bunch of useless people.

359
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:48,680
However,

360
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:49,880
Li Ming is dead.

361
00:20:50,320 --> 00:20:51,640
Li Ming is dead?

362
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:52,000
Yes.

363
00:20:54,440 --> 00:20:56,840
What's the use of killing him?

364
00:20:57,520 --> 00:20:58,760
Where are they now?

365
00:20:59,000 --> 00:20:59,920
Still in Yang City.

366
00:21:00,640 --> 00:21:03,280
Do we need to send more people?

367
00:21:03,280 --> 00:21:04,200
What do you think?

368
00:21:07,240 --> 00:21:07,760
Chancellor.

369
00:21:08,120 --> 00:21:09,080
Prince Heqin is here.

370
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:13,640
I can't believe he's still alive.

371
00:21:14,840 --> 00:21:15,720
What about Wan?

372
00:21:18,040 --> 00:21:18,560
Quick.

373
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:19,560
Let him in.

374
00:21:19,560 --> 00:21:20,040
Yes.

375
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:28,600
Your Grace.

376
00:21:29,360 --> 00:21:30,480
No need to be so formal.

377
00:21:31,100 --> 00:21:31,860
Please sit.

378
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:33,080
Your Grace,

379
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:34,040
please have a seat.

380
00:21:44,600 --> 00:21:45,840
I wonder what's the purpose

381
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:47,760
of Your Grace's visit

382
00:21:48,520 --> 00:21:49,760
to my residence today.

383
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:51,000
I came here today

384
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:54,760
to negotiate a deal with chancellor.

385
00:21:55,480 --> 00:21:56,320
A deal?

386
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:01,680
I'm not sure what I can really do

387
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:02,800
for Your Grace?

388
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:06,800
You can leave first.

389
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:23,440
I want to...

390
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:35,720
be the Emperor of Qi Kingdom.

391
00:22:44,560 --> 00:22:46,760
Your Grace must be kidding me.

392
00:22:48,160 --> 00:22:49,440
I'll just pretend as if Your Grace

393
00:22:49,440 --> 00:22:50,800
has never been to my residence before.

394
00:22:50,800 --> 00:22:52,320
Besides I've never heard

395
00:22:52,320 --> 00:22:53,840
Your Grace say anything like this.

396
00:22:53,840 --> 00:22:54,600
Your Grace,

397
00:22:55,040 --> 00:22:55,840
please leave.

398
00:22:58,760 --> 00:23:00,040
Chancellor, you don't
need to pretend anymore.

399
00:23:01,680 --> 00:23:03,120
Your goals and mine are the same.

400
00:23:04,040 --> 00:23:05,680
I can give you a hand.

401
00:23:06,080 --> 00:23:09,840
Are you slandering me for treason?

402
00:23:10,120 --> 00:23:11,320
Your Grace.

403
00:23:11,760 --> 00:23:13,320
Joking about things like this
that can get you killed

404
00:23:13,320 --> 00:23:15,520
is definitely not allowed.

405
00:23:15,880 --> 00:23:17,000
Do you know

406
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:21,200
that Wan is already
dead in the pirate's lair?

407
00:23:22,160 --> 00:23:23,160
Wan?

408
00:23:24,840 --> 00:23:26,080
Wasn't she with His Majesty

409
00:23:26,080 --> 00:23:27,880
in the summer palace?

410
00:23:28,280 --> 00:23:29,160
It's all because of Qi Yan.

411
00:23:31,040 --> 00:23:32,560
He wasn't even in the summer palace.

412
00:23:33,360 --> 00:23:35,080
He left Wan in the summer palace

413
00:23:35,720 --> 00:23:37,160
and that's how she was
captured by the pirates.

414
00:23:37,800 --> 00:23:38,640
So,

415
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:41,680
it was the pirates who killed Wan?

416
00:23:42,160 --> 00:23:45,280
These people are ruthless.

417
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:46,200
No.

418
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:50,080
It wasn't the pirates.

419
00:23:51,440 --> 00:23:53,480
It was Qi Yan who killed Wan.

420
00:23:54,600 --> 00:23:56,640
He knew the pirates had taken Wan.

421
00:23:57,760 --> 00:23:59,080
Instead of rescuing her,

422
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:01,480
he sent someone to kill her

423
00:24:02,400 --> 00:24:03,840
for his own reputation.

424
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:06,000
I must avenge

425
00:24:07,040 --> 00:24:08,800
this blood feud!

426
00:24:10,280 --> 00:24:11,680
Please, chancellor.

427
00:24:12,560 --> 00:24:14,160
Assist me.

428
00:24:14,880 --> 00:24:16,760
Wan...

429
00:24:23,120 --> 00:24:25,480
I lost Ying before.

430
00:24:25,480 --> 00:24:27,680
Now I've lost Wan.

431
00:24:28,560 --> 00:24:31,960
Why is my life so miserable?

432
00:24:37,520 --> 00:24:38,920
To be honest,

433
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:43,000
I was planning to take Wan
with me and leave before.

434
00:24:45,120 --> 00:24:46,120
But now...

435
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:51,520
I really owe Wan too much.

436
00:24:54,040 --> 00:24:56,640
I'm truly grateful

437
00:24:57,080 --> 00:25:00,160
for your devotion to my little girl.

438
00:25:01,440 --> 00:25:04,480
I'm in such deep pain right now.

439
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:06,560
My mind is blank with grief.

440
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:12,920
May Your Grace allow me
some time to recover

441
00:25:13,280 --> 00:25:17,000
and think carefully before
reporting back to you.

442
00:25:17,280 --> 00:25:18,560
Please, Your Grace.

443
00:25:19,280 --> 00:25:20,480
Chancellor Cui.

444
00:25:21,680 --> 00:25:22,760
Please accept my condolences.

445
00:25:23,880 --> 00:25:25,840
Wan...

446
00:25:27,240 --> 00:25:28,960
Wan...

447
00:25:40,800 --> 00:25:42,560
His Majesty has been away
in the summer palace for so long.

448
00:25:42,560 --> 00:25:43,680
He's back finally.

449
00:25:44,120 --> 00:25:45,000
However,

450
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:46,920
why is the palanquin so tightly covered?

451
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:49,360
I heard His Majesty
caught an illness outside the palace.

452
00:25:49,360 --> 00:25:50,600
It's contagious.

453
00:25:51,760 --> 00:25:52,960
Do you want to be dead?

454
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:59,200
It seems like chancellor has acted.

455
00:26:02,120 --> 00:26:04,160
I only had one daughter.

456
00:26:04,160 --> 00:26:05,800
This feud must be repaid.

457
00:26:06,560 --> 00:26:08,000
Please rest assured, Your Grace.

458
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:10,200
I will do my utmost

459
00:26:10,200 --> 00:26:11,480
to assist you.

460
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:12,760
Thank you, Chancellor.

461
00:26:27,560 --> 00:26:28,200
Chancellor.

462
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:31,000
Doesn't it seem too easy

463
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:32,240
to win over Prince Heqin?

464
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:36,000
No matter what he's up to,

465
00:26:36,520 --> 00:26:38,280
let's just wait and see.

466
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:41,280
Let him deal with His Majesty.

467
00:26:41,280 --> 00:26:44,080
As for us, we'll be
the fisherman who profits.

468
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:45,240
Yes.

469
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:46,840
Chancellor is really thoughtful.

470
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:53,000
Freshly baked pastries!

471
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:54,880
Come and taste! Take a look!

472
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:56,080
Here!

473
00:26:56,080 --> 00:26:56,880
Take a look!

474
00:26:56,880 --> 00:26:58,040
Free samples!

475
00:26:58,040 --> 00:26:59,640
Also, packaged ones!

476
00:26:59,960 --> 00:27:01,180
Come and take a look!

477
00:27:01,180 --> 00:27:02,040
[Pastries]

478
00:27:02,040 --> 00:27:02,880
Come, Master!

479
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:03,680
Take a look!

480
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:04,960
You can give it to a friend as a gift.

481
00:27:06,200 --> 00:27:07,440
Are you buying for someone?

482
00:27:10,000 --> 00:27:12,160
It's for a girl you like, right?

483
00:27:13,720 --> 00:27:15,200
What flavor does she like?

484
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:16,760
Sweet or sour?

485
00:27:17,040 --> 00:27:17,640
Sweet.

486
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:20,920
Try this one.

487
00:27:26,520 --> 00:27:27,280
How is it?

488
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:28,560
I'll take a packet of these.

489
00:27:28,560 --> 00:27:29,280
Okay.

490
00:27:30,760 --> 00:27:31,320
Two packets!

491
00:27:31,760 --> 00:27:32,280
Sure!

492
00:27:32,280 --> 00:27:33,800
I'll wrap them up for you right away.

493
00:27:38,120 --> 00:27:39,360
His Majesty is back.

494
00:27:40,240 --> 00:27:41,600
Surely Kong An is back too.

495
00:27:42,360 --> 00:27:43,880
I wonder what he'll bring me.

496
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:47,240
Once I've delivered
the talismans to the Empress,

497
00:27:47,240 --> 00:27:48,480
I can go find Kong An.

498
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:52,440
Your Highness.

499
00:27:53,600 --> 00:27:54,560
Your Highness.

500
00:27:57,760 --> 00:27:59,720
How is His Majesty's illness?

501
00:28:00,120 --> 00:28:02,120
I was stopped when I'd just arrived

502
00:28:02,120 --> 00:28:03,160
at His Majesty's chamber.

503
00:28:05,120 --> 00:28:06,040
Who stopped you?

504
00:28:06,280 --> 00:28:07,280
It was the Imperial Guards.

505
00:28:07,280 --> 00:28:08,880
Why did the Imperial Guards stop you?

506
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:10,000
Reporting to the Your Highness,

507
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:11,120
Chancellor Cui requests a meeting.

508
00:28:21,560 --> 00:28:22,160
Brother.

509
00:28:24,080 --> 00:28:26,600
Why are the Imperial Guards
guarding Yan's chamber?

510
00:28:30,080 --> 00:28:30,800
You may leave.

511
00:28:30,800 --> 00:28:31,440
Yes.

512
00:28:39,280 --> 00:28:41,800
That's because His Majesty
isn't actually in the palace.

513
00:28:42,040 --> 00:28:43,760
His Majesty's return
to the palace due to an illness

514
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:46,760
was just a scheme I arranged.

515
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:49,760
So where is Yan now?

516
00:28:49,760 --> 00:28:52,120
He secretly went to Yang City
from the summer palace.

517
00:28:52,280 --> 00:28:53,160
Moreover,

518
00:28:54,600 --> 00:28:56,600
he won't be coming back.

519
00:28:57,080 --> 00:28:58,000
What do you mean?

520
00:28:58,360 --> 00:29:00,600
He has leverage over me.

521
00:29:00,840 --> 00:29:02,080
If he were to return,

522
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:04,080
the Cui family would be
completely finished.

523
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:06,040
Brother.

524
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:07,400
You've lost your mind.

525
00:29:07,760 --> 00:29:09,920
He's the backbone of our Cui family.

526
00:29:10,320 --> 00:29:12,160
You've watched him grow up.

527
00:29:13,200 --> 00:29:14,360
No matter what you've done,

528
00:29:14,640 --> 00:29:16,800
I can help you persuade him.

529
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:18,880
Will he listen to you?

530
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:20,000
Besides,

531
00:29:20,720 --> 00:29:22,040
can you really blame this on me

532
00:29:22,040 --> 00:29:23,200
for this situation?

533
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:25,160
Who in this world doesn't know

534
00:29:25,160 --> 00:29:26,480
that half of Qi's territory

535
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:28,120
was conquered by our Cui family.

536
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:30,560
Even the former Emperor said

537
00:29:30,560 --> 00:29:31,880
that the Empress of the Qi family

538
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:33,400
must be the Cui family's

539
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:34,160
daughter.

540
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:35,320
However,

541
00:29:35,720 --> 00:29:37,280
look at how he treats Wan now.

542
00:29:37,600 --> 00:29:38,280
That's why,

543
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:40,120
I'm running out of

544
00:29:40,640 --> 00:29:42,280
patience with this person.

545
00:29:42,560 --> 00:29:43,360
Brother,

546
00:29:43,520 --> 00:29:45,320
please tell me where Yan is.

547
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:46,400
For the sake of the nation
and the people,

548
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:47,400
please spare him!

549
00:29:47,840 --> 00:29:48,280
Brother.

550
00:29:48,280 --> 00:29:48,840
Who is there?

551
00:29:51,360 --> 00:29:52,560
You stay here.

552
00:29:52,800 --> 00:29:53,960
Take your time to think it through.

553
00:29:53,960 --> 00:29:54,440
Brother.

554
00:30:02,840 --> 00:30:03,360
Chancellor.

555
00:30:05,520 --> 00:30:06,680
Who just came?

556
00:30:06,920 --> 00:30:08,000
It was a palace maid
from the Lingtai Pavilion.

557
00:30:08,320 --> 00:30:09,840
She said she came to deliver
talismans to the Empress.

558
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:11,400
She also said that the talismans
for today must not be delayed.

559
00:30:11,720 --> 00:30:12,720
So I let her in.

560
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:13,920
Where is she?

561
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:14,600
She just left.

562
00:30:14,600 --> 00:30:15,680
Then why don't you
hurry and go after her?

563
00:30:15,680 --> 00:30:16,280
Yes.

564
00:30:16,280 --> 00:30:16,800
Wait.

565
00:30:19,080 --> 00:30:21,320
Remember, don't leave anyone alive.

566
00:30:21,500 --> 00:30:22,200
Yes.

567
00:30:22,200 --> 00:30:22,840
Let's go.

568
00:30:22,840 --> 00:30:25,680
[Shoukang Palace]

569
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:26,480
Listen up.

570
00:30:27,920 --> 00:30:29,720
The Empress isn't feeling well lately

571
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:31,320
and needs to rest in the chamber.

572
00:30:31,320 --> 00:30:33,640
No one except me is allowed to see her.

573
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:34,600
Yes.

574
00:30:42,320 --> 00:30:43,920
I'll be leaving the palace for a while.

575
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:45,720
What do you want?

576
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:46,840
I'll bring it back to you.

577
00:30:46,840 --> 00:30:48,240
Just bring me some delicious food.

578
00:30:55,320 --> 00:30:56,000
I'm going to leave now.

579
00:30:57,480 --> 00:30:58,560
I'll come find you when I'm back.

580
00:31:00,200 --> 00:31:00,880
Guard Kong.

581
00:31:03,200 --> 00:31:04,720
The question you asked me today,

582
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:05,960
I already have the answer.

583
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:07,880
What is it?

584
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:10,760
I'll tell you when you come back.

585
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:24,920
I need to leave the palace quickly

586
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:26,520
and inform His Majesty
of Chancellor Cui's plans.

587
00:31:27,840 --> 00:31:28,320
Let's go.

588
00:31:34,760 --> 00:31:35,480
What's going on?

589
00:31:35,480 --> 00:31:36,280
Why are you in such a rush?

590
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:37,160
Token.

591
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:43,200
She's there

592
00:31:44,520 --> 00:31:45,160
stop her immediately.

593
00:31:45,160 --> 00:31:46,080
Don't let her escape.

594
00:31:46,680 --> 00:31:47,840
- Catch her!
- Stop her, quickly!

595
00:31:47,840 --> 00:31:49,400
Stop her, quickly!

596
00:32:01,920 --> 00:32:02,800
Sorry.

597
00:32:07,700 --> 00:32:11,660
[May the blessing be upon you]

598
00:32:13,720 --> 00:32:15,600
Where did you go
so early in the morning?

599
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:18,160
Don't you know we're packing up
to return to the capital today?

600
00:32:19,280 --> 00:32:21,240
Who are you bringing
all these packages for?

601
00:32:21,560 --> 00:32:22,160
Are these food?

602
00:32:22,520 --> 00:32:23,240
Share some with me.

603
00:32:25,280 --> 00:32:26,680
Look at how stingy you are.

604
00:32:30,360 --> 00:32:31,200
I can't believe

605
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:33,160
I brought so much stuff with me.

606
00:32:33,680 --> 00:32:35,160
Now there are just a few things left.

607
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:44,760
Mengmeng.

608
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:49,360
This is from Lu Huan.

609
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:51,720
He found it while sorting
through Minister Li's belongings.

610
00:32:56,520 --> 00:32:57,400
Do you want to take a look?

611
00:33:02,580 --> 00:33:04,460
[Watercourse Plan]

612
00:33:04,480 --> 00:33:05,600
What's this?

613
00:33:05,600 --> 00:33:07,400
These are some of Minister Li's

614
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,440
specific plans about the watercourse.

615
00:33:10,820 --> 00:33:13,660
[Your subject Li Ming
bows to thank Your Majesty]

616
00:33:17,600 --> 00:33:19,600
If Minister Li's watercourse plans

617
00:33:19,600 --> 00:33:20,760
can be implemented,

618
00:33:21,120 --> 00:33:23,040
it'll surely benefit the people.

619
00:33:23,240 --> 00:33:23,760
I

620
00:33:24,560 --> 00:33:26,360
will definitely fulfill
Minister Li's wishes,

621
00:33:26,960 --> 00:33:28,080
make the canal navigable.

622
00:33:28,480 --> 00:33:29,680
Let the people know

623
00:33:30,600 --> 00:33:31,520
what an extraordinary person

624
00:33:31,520 --> 00:33:32,680
Minister Li was.

625
00:33:37,780 --> 00:33:41,020
[Gathering blessings and prosperity]

626
00:33:41,720 --> 00:33:42,720
I'll head back to my room first.

627
00:33:57,160 --> 00:33:58,760
Why is it raining again?

628
00:34:01,280 --> 00:34:01,920
Rain...

629
00:34:03,080 --> 00:34:05,440
It was raining the day
I arrived in Qi Kingdom.

630
00:34:06,600 --> 00:34:07,440
Perhaps...

631
00:34:21,680 --> 00:34:23,000
What's going on here?

632
00:34:45,500 --> 00:34:48,740
♪When a gust of wind brushes past♪

633
00:34:48,740 --> 00:34:52,300
♪The sand and wind burn with passion♪

634
00:34:52,300 --> 00:34:55,380
♪Unafraid to forego a chance
to quench our thirst♪

635
00:34:55,380 --> 00:34:59,180
♪Like camels walking with eyes closed♪

636
00:34:59,180 --> 00:35:02,300
♪When the rain falls
into a rare silence♪

637
00:35:02,300 --> 00:35:06,020
♪Thinking of hardships
you and I don't know♪

638
00:35:06,020 --> 00:35:09,020
♪No need to hum the wind's song♪

639
00:35:09,020 --> 00:35:13,100
♪Uncaring of the darkening skies♪

640
00:35:13,100 --> 00:35:14,780
♪I understood all that for you♪

641
00:35:14,780 --> 00:35:16,540
♪But you have disappeared♪

642
00:35:16,540 --> 00:35:18,220
♪I am lost in the dark♪

643
00:35:18,220 --> 00:35:19,940
♪How should I stop?♪

644
00:35:19,940 --> 00:35:21,620
♪Loving you feels like another lifetime♪

645
00:35:21,620 --> 00:35:25,300
♪But yearning flows into a poem♪

646
00:35:25,300 --> 00:35:28,260
♪For us to meet again♪

647
00:35:28,260 --> 00:35:31,620
♪Requires the promise of millennia♪

648
00:35:31,620 --> 00:35:33,860
♪Watching the rain hail down♪

649
00:35:33,860 --> 00:35:38,940
♪It's like you're still beside me♪

650
00:35:38,940 --> 00:35:41,900
♪When I want to cross over♪

651
00:35:41,900 --> 00:35:45,980
♪To touch you♪

652
00:35:45,980 --> 00:35:48,420
♪But I can't see your fading face♪

653
00:35:48,420 --> 00:35:52,700
♪On the opposite shore♪

654
00:35:52,700 --> 00:35:55,700
♪How do I voice this?♪

655
00:35:55,700 --> 00:35:59,100
♪My heart beats uneasily♪

656
00:35:59,100 --> 00:36:02,020
♪How I long to hold tight♪

657
00:36:02,020 --> 00:36:06,380
♪To the loneliness in your hands♪

658
00:36:06,380 --> 00:36:09,380
♪Yet you warn me♪

659
00:36:09,380 --> 00:36:13,420
♪Any closer and I'll set in stone♪

660
00:36:13,420 --> 00:36:15,020
♪The sunset deep in your heart♪

661
00:36:15,020 --> 00:36:22,900
♪Of the day you most loved me♪
